  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2011-11-03",
    "date": "2011-12-15T20:13:28Z",
    "text": "Help Inspire and Retrain our Exceptional Veterans Act of 2011 or HIRE Veterans Act of 2011 - Directs the Secretary of Commerce to establish a program to award grants to local chambers of commerce to provide veterans with apprenticeships and career advice. Prohibits more than one grant from being awarded to a local chamber during each five-year period. Provides individual grant amounts of at least $10,000 and not more than $20,000. Terminates the grant program at the end of FY2022.\n\nRequires an annual report from the Secretary to Congress after each year of the grant program."
  },
